    "causal_summary": "This penalty was added on the assumption that reranking is load-bearing. The arc 008 benchmarks haven't actually validated that assumption against the OFF baseline; they've validated specific rerankers (Qwen, ms-marco) against each other. The ms-marco bench's −6 hits below OFF is the strongest signal that **positional fallback may already be good enough** for this corpus.",
